subsection.def:
customer
                    (客戶) means any person having a banking
                account or other dealing, transaction or arrangement with Chekiang First Bank;

existing
                    (現有) means existing, outstanding or in force
                immediately before the appointed day;

liabilities
                    (法律責任) includes duties and obligations of
                every description (whether present or future, actual or contingent);

will
                    (遺囑) includes a codicil and any other
                testamentary writing;
